    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>New World hardwood derived from several species of the Swartzia genus, having a dark reddish brown, purplish, or nearly black heartwood and pale yellowish white sapwood that is sharply demarcated.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
